snippet.title: Cyber Manhunt: New World - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cyber Manhunt: New World is a narrative-driven puzzle game developed by Aluba Studio. Players will embody an AI assistant within a major company tasked with deploying social engineering tactics to expose specific truths to the world. Cyber Manhunt: New World is launching at a later date for PC with a Steam demo available now through December 15.

#CyberManhuntNewWorld
